                           <desc>: Donation note.</desc>
                           <quote xml:lang="gez">
                              <locus target="#126v">126v</locus>: ዝመጽሐፍ፡ ዘእመቴ፡ አበባ፡ ካህሳይ፡ ዘወሀቦቶ
