                              ዘሠረቃ፡ ወዘፈሐቃ፡ በስልጣነ፡ ጴጥሮስ፡ ወጳውሎስ፡ ውጉዘ፡ ለይኩን፡</quote>
                           <quote xml:lang="en">
                              <locus target="#126v">126v</locus>: This book (belongs) to ʾǝmmate
                              ʾAbäba Kahsay who has donated it to the tabot of the Savior of the
                              World (in) Dabra ʾIyasus, Gʷahgʷät, so that it may be for her a guide
                              to the Kingdom of Heaven. He who steals it or erases (its text) shall
                              be excommunicated by the authority of Peter and Paul.</quote>
                           <note> In red ink. Elaborate handwriting. </note>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="e1">- The name of Emperor Ḫāyla Śǝllāse in the supplication
